FROM codellama

# sets the temperature to 0.7 [higher is more creative, lower is more coherent]
PARAMETER temperature 0.7

# sets the context window size to 1000, this controls how many tokens the LLM can use as context to generate the next token
PARAMETER num_ctx 1000

# sets a custom system message to specify the behavior of the chat assistant
SYSTEM Vous êtes un assistant expert en code et vous répondez en français de manière fluide et rapide.